More project specific rules and context:
This website is front-end only and serverless. 
This website is a tool designed to overcome executive dysfunction by asking questions and leading to an helpful resolution.
This is implemented as a decision tree to help with decision paralysis. 
This tree is called a deck (component Deck), cards (component Card) being a some text information and some items (CardItem) to read or pick from, leading to other cards.
All UI text should be supporting multiple language using i18n.
We use Ajv for json schema validation.
